# Node.js

## Run a js program
```js
node program.js
```
## Add custom modules to a project

```js
npm install -g <ModuleName>
```

**add it to package.json automatically**
```js
npm install <ModuleName> --save //--save-exact can be added if the version need to be exactly this one (better for production app)
```

## Pass arguments to a js program

```js
node program.js arg1 arg2 arg3
//Get the arg
var arg1 = process.argv[2];
var arg2 = process.argv[3];
var arg3 = process.argv[4];
//Because the first arg is "node" and the second is "program.js"
```
